sources.description:
An unknown terror stalks a ski resort!
A Colorado ski resort is besieged by a sub-human beast that commits brutal murders on the slopes.

Original title: Snowbeast (1977) AKA Bigfoot
Director: Herb Wallerstein
Writer: Joseph Stefano 
Cast: Bo Svenson, Yvette Mimieux, Robert Logan, Clint Walker
Genre: Horror
